The application of scanning electron microscopy (SEM) in nanoscience is of great importance to study the surface morphology of synthesized nanoparticles. The morphology and size determined from scanning electron microscopy (SEM) image showed that carbon quantum dots are quasi- spherical with size 40 nm (Fig. 5
                        ) and ZnO/CQDs nanocomposites have 14 nm showed in Fig. 6
                        .
